  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Stimulating overnight muscle protein synthesis, might augment muscle hypertrophy, increase
      mitochondrial mass, and/or improve muscle tissue repair. The goal of this proposal will be to
      provide further insight into the responsiveness of the muscle protein synthetic machinery to
      food intake in relation to age.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
